definitions.title: n.f.
definitions.body: branch, bough, metaph. of Israel under figure of olive tree [[דָּֽלִיּוֹתָיו]] Je 11:16 Ez Eze 17:6, Eze 17:7 (figure of vine); v:Eze 17:23. (under figure of cedar); Eze 31:7, Eze 31:9, Eze 31:12 of Asshur as a cedar, [[דָּלִיּׂתָיו]] Ez Eze 19:11 Isr. as a vine (cf. Löw: 65).
